            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3EJob%2028%3A1-30%3A31%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22job_28_1%22%20bk%3D%22job%22%20ch%3D%2228%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3EJob%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E28%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EJob%20Speaks%20of%20Wisdom%20and%20Understanding%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BPeople%20know%20where%20to%20mine%20silver%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20how%20to%20refine%20gold.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22job_28_2%22%20bk%3D%22job%22%20ch%3D%2228%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3EThey%20know%20where%20to%20dig%20iron%20from%20the%20earth%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20how%20to%20smelt%20copper%20from%20rock.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22job_28_3%22%20bk%3D%22job%22%20ch%3D%2228%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3EThey%20know%20how%20to%20shine%20light%20in%20the%20darkness%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20explore%20the%20farthest%20regions%20of%20the%20earth%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eas%20they%20search%20in%20the%20dark%20for%20ore.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22job_28_4%22%20bk%3D%22job%22%20ch%3D%2228%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3EThey%20sink%20a%20mine%20shaft%20into%20the%20earth%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Efar%20from%20where%20anyone%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EThey%20descend%20on%20ropes%2C%20swinging%20back%20and%20forth.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C